Rangeley slow and melodic transition in

distorted very busy

all that special or distinct especially
at the end of this album so overall
while a thousand gaks and the tree of
clues is not a perfect record it's not a
perfect remix album I do think this is a
wonderful companion piece to the
original 1000x
building on the bizarre and unique
